message.body: Morninggg! I have your red notebook, you left it at whetzels
Oh thanks!!! How did that end up there? And I think I'm dying...
We were using it for rules for kings cup! Omgggg yeah I can't imagine how shitty you must feel haha
Oh ya!!!! Miserable. I am so hungover.
:( everything was so much fun until like the very end of the night
I don't even remember it... I remember beer ping and vaguely remember kings cup then nothing lol
You left shortly after kings cup! We sat on the couch with emma for a while and then waited outside for your roommate. You kept telling me to go inside lol
Lol I don't remember that.... But thanks for waiting with me hahahahaha
